{"comments":"Resource Registry — Central Management for GPU Resources\n\n## Purpose\n\nThe registry is the single source of truth for all GPU resources:\n\n- **Unified access**: Single point for pipelines, buffers, textures\n- **Frame tracking**: Enables LRU eviction and garbage collection\n- **Memory budgeting**: Monitor and limit total resource usage\n\n## Lifecycle Management\n\n- Tracks frame number for LRU eviction\n- Garbage collection removes unused resources\n- Single source of truth for resource state\n\n## At Billion-Agent Scale\n\nThe registry enables efficient resource sharing:\n- Agents query the registry before allocation\n- Frame-based tracking enables predictable eviction\n- Memory budgets prevent runaway allocation\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["pipelines",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","Resource","Pipeline"],"PipelineCache"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["buffers",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","Resource","Buffer"],"BufferPool"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["textures",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","Resource","Texture"],"TexturePool"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["currentFrame",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["gcThreshold",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[116,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Resource/Registry.purs","start":[110,26]},"title":"ResourceRegistry"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotati